mise."],[6402,6468,"Hey."],[6598,6760,"Hey, what’s wrong?"],[7328,7532,"Hey, you’re too handsome"],[7532,7803,"and too rich to be this sad."],[7870,8024,"You think I’m handsome?"],[9609,9693,"I just happen to think"],[9693,9813,"you’re the most gorgeous girl"],[9813,9868,"I’ve ever seen"],[9868,9955,"in my entire life."]],"15":[[1242,1322,"Oh, wait."],[1493,1522,"What?"],[1522,1651,"I can't."],[1651,1835,"Oh, wait. Why?"],[1835,1901,"Why not?"],[1901,1976,"I'm sorry."],[1976,2056,"I just..."],[2260,2331,"I've never done"],[2331,2431,"this before."],[2635,2765,"I guess I've..."],[2831,2923,"I’ve just been waiting."],[2986,3073,"Oh."],[3215,3324,"Waiting for..."],[3324,3390,"for what?"],[3390,3453,"Marriage?"],[3474,3545,"No."],[3603,3682,"No, it's not that."],[3682,3749,"It's just..."],[3807,3962,"I don't know why, but..."],[4033,4149,"no matter who I’m with,"],[4149,4241,"or where I'm at,"],[4387,4446,"I always feel"],[4446,4537,"like there's"],[4621,4717,"someone."],[4867,4917,"Someone who's"],[4917,4963,"supposed to be"],[4963,5100,"the love of my life."],[5326,5367,"I guess I'm"],[5367,5492,"just waiting for him."],[5784,5880,"Wait."],[5997,6076,"Cameron."],[6160,6222,"This scar."]],"16":[[33,166,"Ow!"],[312,563,"Wait, Mads. Wait."],[654,796,"Are you okay? What’s going on?"],[796,867,"It’s..."],[913,1067,"It’s my memories."],[1376,1497,"When I was eight,"],[1630,1739,"I got into this accident"],[1739,1818,"at the orphanage."],[1972,2160,"Apparently, I lost a significant amount"],[2160,2239,"of memories, because of"],[2239,2293,"some sort of..."],[2431,2527,"brain damage."],[2869,2927,"Right."],[3032,3132,"I’m sorry about that."],[3161,3244,"Don’t be."],[3937,4045,"Whatever I forgot,"],[4170,4312,"it must have been pretty painful."],[4421,4521,"Growing up,"],[4521,4571,"all I knew was"],[4571,4717,"this feeling of abandonment."],[4842,5021,"This feeling like I didn’t matter"],[5021,5113,"to anyone."],[5372,5484,"I can do without more pain"],[5484,5580,"from the past."],[6535,6623,"Mads, there’s something"],[6623,6698,"I need to tell you."],[6852,7011,"You were an orphan too, right?"],[7223,7336,"Tell me about that."],[7374,7670,"Yeah. Right. About that."],[7695,7862,"So, when I was younger,"],[7899,8045,"and I was living in the orphanage,"],[8045,8162,"there was this girl there."],[8258,8379,"And I was..."],[8379,8637,"I was completely in-"],[8812,8967,"I mean, she..."],[9042,9184,"She meant everything to me."],[9355,9818,"And then, one day, I had to leave her."],[9909,10060,"I didn’t have a choice."],[10264,10481,"I got adopted and she didn’t."],[10556,10802,"I went back there to find her,"],[10802,10902,"to look for her."],[10906,11094,"You know, I would take her over"],[11119,11428,"some rich family any day."],[11498,11644,"But then something happened to her."],[11878,12028,"It was all my fault."],[12141,12437,"If I just fought like a little harder..."],[12491,12587,"to go back there."],[12587,12670,"If I had just..."],[12737,12892,"ran away with her, then..."],[12933,13058,"then maybe you wouldn’t have"],[13058,13200,"forgotten about... me,"],[13275,13400,"Mads."]],"17":[[400,521,"As long as I'm here with you,"],[521,617,"nothing else matters."],[1976,2043,"Coach Forgrave."],[2043,2139,"Sorry for calling so late."],[2164,2277,"No problem, son."],[2277,2352,"Have you considered"],[2352,2431,"my offer?"],[2431,2489,"Yes."],[2627,2711,"I accept."],[2844,2936,"I will come play for the"],[2936,3061,"Central University Knights as"],[3061,3157,"your starting quarterback."]],"18":[[1522,1589,"I can't believe"],[1589,1689,"we almost hooked up."],[1739,1860,"I just met the guy."],[1972,2072,"Even though"],[2135,2210,"every part of"],[2210,2306,"him feels so..."],[2477,2581,"familiar."],[2977,3078,"Damn, Mads."],[3148,3336,"Can you at least buy me dinner first?"],[3787,3912,"Good Morning."],[4195,4325,"Look, I gotta get going."],[4325,4379,"Home?"],[4496,4621,"Oh. Right."],[4621,4771,"It’s not like you go to my school"],[4771,4825,